{"tid":2051014,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"從堪輿學角度分析熱血公民落選原因","createTime":"2020-06-04T12:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T15:22:09.000Z","uid":38189,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"33e70c209c19eeb58083ae1df1086bdb77a4b483","tid":2051014,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:54:25.000Z","msg":"作者：N賓<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知 熱狗全名熱血公民 熱=屬火 <br />\n上屆立法會熱狗出戰五區<br />\n分別有 鄭錦滿 黃洋達 陳雲 黃毓民 鄭松泰<br />\n當選嘅有 鄭松泰<br />\n點解呢？<br />\n松=木，木生火，自然旺熱血公民<br />\n落選又有邊個呢？<br />\n鄭錦滿 <br />\n黃洋達 <br />\n滿，洋=水，水剋火<br />\n落選係必然嘅事<br />\n而陳雲 雲生雨 雨為水 水火不容 <br />\n自然會落選<br />\n黃毓民呢？<br />\n個名睇落係冇水 但你查查<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skBOESU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskBOESU.jpg&h=9de8cf08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就知落選原因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年推測熱狗派出 法子 黃兆健 鄭錦滿 黃洋達<br />\n我賓屈指推算<br />\n法子，法從水，水剋火 落選<br />\n黃兆健 55波<br />\n後面兩件垃圾唔使提<br />\n總結：估計熱狗全線仆街。<br />\n<br />\n利申：樓主為賴布衣39代傳人 準確率有85％"},{"pid":"496d22c5ff0b0e2dedc1a10d9b73d53ddbb55bea","tid":2051014,"uid":8968,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"好心幫樓主總結一下<br />\n<br />\n結果：熱狗是垃圾"},{"pid":"cd0720305798ccf0d7880a80bb132f030c28e675","tid":2051014,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"呢個係政黨宣傳po，唔想睇可以上一頁"},{"pid":"59c460e46abaf2fd3e6c2e61c949e82b42c52fcb","tid":2051014,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"496d22c5ff0b0e2dedc1a10d9b73d53ddbb55bea","tid":2051014,"uid":8968,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"好心幫樓主總結一下<br />\n<br />\n結果：熱狗是垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"未必，賓有辦法破解"},{"pid":"bcacb41c438731aabc294c6e386948729b49567e","tid":2051014,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59c460e46abaf2fd3e6c2e61c949e82b42c52fcb","tid":2051014,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid